Hints for Using Licq

o  Change your status by right clicking on the status label.
o  View system messages by selecting your alias from the system menu
   or by double clicking on the message label.
o  Change groups simply by right clicking on the status label.
o  Use Ctrl-M to toggle mini-mode, Ctrl-X to exit, Ctrl-H to hide,
   and Ctrl-I to view the next message.
